Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:13.24,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}見渡す夢の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:13.24,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}眺望著夢想的痕跡
